{"word":"H7270 - רָגַל - râgal - raw-gal' - Backbite","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָגַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râgal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-gal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Backbite"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேவுகாரர், புறங்கூறு, வேவுபார், உளவுபார், வீண்பழி, நடக்கப்பழக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to go on foot, to spy out, to foot it, to go about, to walk along, to move the feet"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be a tale - bearer, to slander, to go about"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to slander"},{"paragraph":"2) to go about as explorer, to spy"},{"paragraph":"c) (Tiphel) to teach to walk"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>walk</i> along; but only in specific applications, to <i>reconnoitre</i>, to <i>be a tale bearer</i> (that is, slander); also (as denominative from <a href=\"#/H7272 - רֶגֶל - regel - reh'-gel/7272\">H7272</a>) to <i>lead about: - </i>backbite, search, slander, (e-) spy (out), teach to go, view."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4772 - מַרְגְלָה - margᵉlâh - mar-ghel-aw'/4772\">H4772</a>, <a href=\"#/H7270 - רָגַל - râgal - raw-gal'/7270\">H7270</a>, <a href=\"#/H7272 - רֶגֶל - regel - reh'-gel/7272\">H7272</a>, <a href=\"#/H7273 - רַגְלִי - raglîy - rag-lee'/7273\">H7273</a>, <a href=\"#/H7274 - רֹגְלִים - Rôgᵉlîym - ro-gel-eem'/7274\">H7274</a>, <a href=\"#/H8637 - תִּרְגַּל - tirgal - teer-gal'/8637\">H8637</a>"}]}